title: History Extra podcast - November 2009 - Part 2
itunes:title: History Extra podcast - November 2009 - Part 2
itunes:subtitle: Sue Elliott explains how the children of the Britons who tended First World War graves at Ypres went on to fight the Nazis. Also in this issue Jeremy Black reveals why the battle of Quiberon 250 years ago saved Britain from invasion.
